item.title: How Does Nebraska Compare, Recruiting Wise, Next To All NCAA Volleyball Teams?
item.description: Nebraska Volleyball has been a staple at the university for years now. The Huskers have consistently stayed ranked throughout the years and have many recognizable alumni. Though they have stayed ranked during the season, how did they look before the season? How did they rank when it came to recruiting classes? Before looking at any data, I need to download my libraries that will help me create all of charts.

item.title: Cleaning up bad football data
item.description: In class, we learned how to take bad text inside of a data file and correct it to clean it up.
